locality: Livingstone Mountains; uninhabited valley near source of Ngolo River, N of summit of Ngolo Mountain and below trail from Luana to Lupingu, in wooded grassland and narrow riverine forest.
S foot of Rungwe Mountain, ca. 2 km N of Nditu and 3.5 km S of Rungwe Crater, in brushland with Hyparrhenia and Kotschya spp.
